{"prompt": "Generate a website for a science-fiction writer. Use a futuristic, midnight blue to evoke mystery.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Sci-Fi Writer's Universe</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-blue: #1A2B4C;\n            --secondary-blue: #3A5B8E;\n            --text-light: #E0E0E0;\n            --text-dark: #A0A0A0;\n            --accent-glow: #6a8cff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace, sans-serif; /* A futuristic-like font */\n            margin: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-blue);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        /* Basic Font Import (using Google Fonts via @import, but for single file, define a fallback) */\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap');\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-blue);\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-blue);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8rem;\n            letter-spacing: 0.15rem;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--accent-glow);\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 2.5rem;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease, text-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-glow);\n            text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent-glow);\n        }\n\n        nav a::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 0;\n            height: 2px;\n            bottom: -5px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            background-color: var(--accent-glow);\n            transition: width 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover::after {\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n\n        main {\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            max-width: 900px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            letter-spacing: 0.1rem;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            padding-top: 6rem;\n            padding-bottom: 6rem;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, #0F1D36 100%);\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-blue);\n            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-out;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; }\n            to { opacity: 1; }\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 1.5rem auto 0;\n            color: var(--text-dark);\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n\n        .work-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2.5rem;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n        }\n\n        .work-card {\n            background-color: #0F1D36;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-blue);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: left;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .work-card::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 4px;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--accent-glow), transparent);\n            transform: translateX(-100%);\n            transition: transform 0.5s ease;\n        }\n\n        .work-card:hover::before {\n            transform: translateX(0);\n        }\n\n        .work-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), 0 0 25px var(--accent-glow);\n        }\n\n        .work-card h3 {\n            color: var(--accent-glow);\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\n            letter-spacing: 0.05rem;\n        }\n\n        .work-card p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            color: var(--text-dark);\n        }\n\n        #contact p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        #contact a {\n            color: var(--accent-glow);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--accent-glow);\n            transition: color 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact a:hover {\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            border-color: var(--text-light);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-blue);\n            color: var(--text-dark);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            border-top: 1px solid var(--secondary-blue);\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.2rem;\n            }\n\n            nav ul {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                gap: 1.5rem;\n            }\n\n            section h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8rem;\n            }\n\n            #hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1rem;\n            }\n\n            .work-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Anya Nova</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#hero\">Home</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#works\">Works</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Connect</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section id=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Journeys Beyond the Known.</h2>\n            <p>Exploring the infinite possibilities of tomorrow, one universe at a time. Welcome to a realm where technology meets the unknown, and humanity faces its ultimate destiny.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"works\">\n            <h2>My Universe of Tales</h2>\n            <div class=\"work-grid\">\n                <div class=\"work-card\">\n                    <h3>Echoes of Sol</h3>\n                    <p>Centuries after Earth's demise, humanity's last hope rests on a relic from a forgotten past. A deep-space scavenger unearths a truth that could either save or doom their scattered civilization.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"work-card\">\n                    <h3>The Chronos Gambit</h3>\n                    <p>Time travel is a reality, but its misuse threatens to unravel existence. A rogue temporal agent must navigate shifting timelines to prevent a paradox that could erase everything.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"work-card\">\n                    <h3>Nebula's Cry</h3>\n                    <p>On a colony world teetering on the edge of rebellion, a young bioscientist discovers a sentient cosmic entity that communicates through dreams, forcing her to choose between her people and an alien intelligence.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Connect with the Cosmos</h2>\n            <p>For inquiries, collaborations, or just to share your thoughts on the future:</p>\n            <p><a href=\"mailto:anya.nova.writes@email.com\">anya.nova.writes@email.com</a></p>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Anya Nova. All Rights Reserved. Data Streams Encrypted.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}